Good preaching so far with the true Word of God. Main complaint - Add the ability to fast forward a sermon. Main reason for this is because you need a network connection to listen and if your connection is cut out, it stops the message and you will have to relisten to the whole thing from the beginning. Next suggestion would be to have the ability to download for offline listening so as to not use lots of data. Otherwise good so far.

Nearly perfect! Thank you guys so much for creating this app, and for adding content on a regular basis. There is one thing I would like to see changed, and then I'll rate it 5 stars. When I'm listening to a message, and I get a text, the message stops, but it doesn't restart, and I have to press the play button again. Sometimes this gets old, particularly if you're on a group text. I'd like the app to start playing after the text notification goes off. Thanks so much!
